The `.hss` container is shaped after the safetensors format
(https://github.com/huggingface/safetensors, Apache-2.0). The optional engine
adapter targets the flash-linear-attention project
(https://github.com/fla-org/flash-linear-attention, MIT). Neither is bundled;
they are referenced for interoperability only.
